author: ForrestKnight
description:
Try out monday.com for free today: https://bit.ly/424DBqu

So you have a lot of unfinished programming projects, huh? Yea, me too. It's something I’ve been dealing with lately.

I have 4 projects I’m actively working on right now and jumping between lol - actually make that 5, I just started another one.

So I’ve done a lot of science-backed research to figure out why this is a thing, so I can know how to combat it, or how to harness it. Why do I keep jumping from project to project? Well, I figured it out and in this video I share it all with you. I hope you enjoy and I hope it helps!
